    "Despite the considerable number of research and development efforts that have been reported to date, many of these efforts are still a long way from being translated into practical applications.",
    "This paper concludes that the use of ML technology for power system protection is still in its early stages.",
    "It identifies significant barriers to implementing ML in power system protection, as described in Section 5.",
    "Unlike many traditional ML problems, these obstacles cannot be easily resolved simply by increasing data or computing power.",
    "Therefore, the necessity to continuously develop understandable and validatable methods in the future is underscored."
